    • Method Detail

      • generateMyName

        private void generateMyName()
        This is a helper method for method update() to be called when the user data has changed and, thus, also the name of the node must be updated.

      • update

        protected void update()
        This method is to be invoked when the user data has changed and the appearance/name of the node requires to be updated. This does not update the visual appearance! Therefore, invoke the tree's updateNode() method.
